plant. Houses filled

00:39:21.160 --> 00:39:23.550
with all kinds of good things you did

00:39:23.560 --> 00:39:27.550
not provide. Wells you did not dig and

00:39:27.560 --> 00:39:30.030
vineyards and olive groves you did not

00:39:30.040 --> 00:39:32.830
plant. Then when you eat and are

00:39:32.840 --> 00:39:34.430
satisfied,

00:39:34.440 --> 00:39:36.390
he said there'll be

00:39:40.200 --> 00:39:43.270
a remnant of you, a

00:39:43.270 --> 00:39:43.280
one percent,

00:39:43.280 --> 00:39:45.510
that this wealth transfer

00:39:45.520 --> 00:39:48.590
is going to be such a blessing

00:39:48.600 --> 00:39:50.110
that you're going to be able to help the

00:39:50.120 --> 00:39:52.150
other people out

00:39:52.160 --> 00:39:55.430
because you listened and obeyed.

00:39:55.440 --> 00:39:57.830
And there will be a wealth transfer

00:39:57.840 --> 00:40:00.550
for houses filled with all kinds of good

00:40:00.560 --> 00:40:01.990
things

00:40:02.000 --> 00:40:04.150
you did not provide. That means you

00:40:04.160 --> 00:40:05.230
didn't have to work for it. It's just

00:40:05.240 --> 00:40:06.910
there. God did it.

00:40:06.920 --> 00:40:09.390
Wells you did not dig. It took

00:40:09.400 --> 00:40:11.790
a long time to dig a well back then

00:40:11.800 --> 00:40:13.430
and get a good one.

00:40:13.430 --> 00:40:13.440
Vineyards—a

00:40:13.440 --> 00:40:15.710
lot of work.

00:40:15.720 --> 00:40:18.830
And olive groves you did not plant.

00:40:18.840 --> 00:40:20.310
You just got it

00:40:20.320 --> 00:40:21.670
because the wealth of the sinner is laid

00:40:21.680 --> 00:40:22.950
up for the righteous.

00:40:22.960 --> 00:40:24.310
That's what He was showing me last

00:40:24.320 --> 00:40:26.390
night. And that was concerning certain

00:40:26.400 --> 00:40:27.950
ministers. I even brought up John

00:40:27.960 --> 00:40:30.350
Kilpatrick. I saw great blessing

00:40:30.360 --> 00:40:33.830
coming on this man and his church.

00:40:33.840 --> 00:40:36.630
I saw certain key members in his church

00:40:36.640 --> 00:40:38.430
last night

00:40:38.440 --> 00:40:40.870
that had invested and they're about to

00:40:40.880 --> 00:40:43.190
come into a lot of money.

00:40:43.200 --> 00:40:45.870
When I was in the spirit, I could see

00:40:45.880 --> 00:40:48.550
this man's church. I am not

00:40:48.560 --> 00:40:50.630
affiliated with him at all.

00:40:50.640 --> 00:40:53.110
I don't know him. I don't even watch

00:40:53.120 --> 00:40:54.950
them. I've watched a couple of his sermons,

00:40:54.960 --> 00:40:58.150
but the Lord brings it up to me.

00:40:58.160 --> 00:41:00.550
I see his face,

00:41:00.560 --> 00:41:02.390
but there's something about him that the

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:04.510
Lord tells me, 'Pray for this man, for his

00:41:04.520 --> 00:41:06.910
health, specifically for him to be

00:41:06.920 --> 00:41:08.790
strong, because God has a plan for his

00:41:08.800 --> 00:41:09.950
life.'But

00:41:09.960 --> 00:41:12.710
He said this to me about this man.

00:41:12.720 --> 00:41:18.310
He gave me Deuteronomy for him.

00:41:18.320 --> 00:41:20.750
And that was concerning his church.

00:41:20.760 --> 00:41:23.070
And the Lord said, 'Lay hold to

00:41:23.070 --> 00:41:23.080
it.'He

00:41:23.080 --> 00:41:25.310
said, 'There's many of you that have not

00:41:25.320 --> 00:41:27.230
been obedient to doing what He's asking

00:41:27.240 --> 00:41:28.630
you to do.

00:41:28.640 --> 00:41:30.550
You've pushed it away. You have a call

00:41:30.560 --> 00:41:32.230
on your life and you've not yielded to

00:41:32.240 --> 00:41:34.550
it.

00:41:34.560 --> 00:41:36.110
You've not been obedient to what God's

00:41:36.120 --> 00:41:38.910
called you to do. It's all hands on deck

00:41:38.920 --> 00:41:40.630
right now.

00:41:40.640 --> 00:41:42.270
For the harvest is plentiful and the

00:41:42.280 --> 00:41:43.950
laborers are few.

00:41:43.960 --> 00:41:46.870
Will you obey what God has called you to

00:41:46.880 --> 00:41:49.470
do in these last days and stop running

00:41:49.480 --> 00:41:52.310
from Him?

00:41:52.320 --> 00:41:54.790
He's going to bypass you and go to the

00:41:54.800 --> 00:41:56.550
next person if you keep putting up your

00:41:56.560 --> 00:41:59.510
hands and say He's out of time.

00:41:59.510 --> 00:41:59.520
He's

00:41:59.520 --> 00:42:01.950
not begging you.

00:42:05.230 --> 00:42:05.240
'You?

00:42:09.600 --> 00:42:12.790
You're only 15. I don't care. Come on.

00:42:12.800 --> 00:42:17.230
How old are you? You're 12. Let's do

00:42:17.230 --> 00:42:17.240
it.'Nothing's

00:42:17.240 --> 00:42:21.030
going to disqualify you.

00:42:21.040 --> 00:42:23.230
Keep underneath the mighty hand of the

00:42:23.240 --> 00:42:25.470
Lord and humble yourself. Keep out of

00:42:25.480 --> 00:42:27.990
sin. Keep yourself right before Him by

00:42:28.000 --> 00:42:30.630
prayer and fasting, seeking Him daily.

00:42:30.640 --> 00:42:33.110
Now, if you fall down in sin, you run to God

00:42:33.120 --> 00:42:34.470
when you sin; you don't run away from

00:42:34.480 --> 00:42:36.510
Him. I'm not saying that

00:42:36.510 --> 00:42:36.520
any

00:42:36.520 --> 00:42:38.790
of us are perfect. But I'm not saying

00:42:38.800 --> 00:42:41.910
you deliberately practice and do

00:42:41.920 --> 00:42:43.470
things that you know you shouldn't be

00:42:43.480 --> 00:42:45.270
doing.

00:42:45.280 --> 00:42:47.670
Now, if you mess up in life and you

00:42:47.680 --> 00:42:49.990
drop a bad word or something,

00:42:50.000 --> 00:42:52.070
people mess up.

00:42:52.080 --> 00:42:53.350
I'm talking about people who are

00:42:53.360 --> 00:42:56.270
deliberately... you know what, bud? Let's go

00:42:56.280 --> 00:42:58.230
to the strip club this weekend and we'll

00:42:58.240 --> 00:43:01.550
repent on Sunday.

00:43:01.560 --> 00:43:03.830
Let's go out and get drunk tonight.

00:43:03.840 --> 00:43:05.870
Let's go get wasted.

00:43:05.880 --> 00:43:07.670
You know that's wrong, but you do it

00:43:07.680 --> 00:43:09.390
because, you know what? It's okay; God

00:43:09.400 --> 00:43:11.750
knows it's under grace.

00:43:11.760 --> 00:43:14.390
You know, it's okay

00:43:14.400 --> 00:43:16.470
to cheat on your wife or husband or

00:43:16.480 --> 00:43:17.750
whatever;

00:43:17.760 --> 00:43:19.870
I'll repent about it. She's

00:43:19.880 --> 00:43:21.390
not fulfilling my needs. He's not

00:43:21.400 --> 00:43:23.230
fulfilling my needs.

00:43:23.240 --> 00:43:24.830
So, I'm just going to go out and, you

00:43:24.840 --> 00:43:26.110
know,

00:43:26.120 --> 00:43:29.030
we have an open marriage; it's cool.

00:43:30.960 --> 00:43:32.310
It's wrong,

00:43:32.320 --> 00:43:37.590
and you know it's wrong,

00:43:37.600 --> 00:43:40.790
but yet you keep dipping in. The

00:43:40.800 --> 00:43:43.190
wages of sin is death,

00:43:43.200 --> 00:43:46.150
and that's what I'm talking about.

00:43:46.160 --> 00:43:48.150
You know it's wrong, and you keep trying.

00:43:48.160 --> 00:43:50.310
You keep doing the same thing over. You

00:43:50.320 --> 00:43:52.550
don't run to God; you run to the

00:43:52.560 --> 00:43:54.310
devil

00:43:54.320 --> 00:43:56.349
and his crowd

00:43:56.359 --> 00:44:01.030
and think, 'Well, I'm saved by grace.

00:44:01.040 --> 00:44:03.390
I can live both sides. One foot

00:44:03.390 --> 00:44:03.400
is

00:44:03.400 --> 00:44:06.030
over here and I have one foot over

00:44:06.030 --> 00:44:06.040
there,

00:44:06.040 --> 00:44:07.310
and we're okay.'And those are the ones I'm

00:44:07.320 --> 00:44:08.950
talking about right now.

00:44:08.960 --> 00:44:11.230
It's time to be all in.

00:44:11.240 --> 00:44:13.950
It's time to sell out for Jesus,

00:44:13.960 --> 00:44:18.110
to look at Him as a holy God,

00:44:18.120 --> 00:44:20.390
and we are made in His image and

00:44:20.400 --> 00:44:24.670
we need to be holy as He is holy.

00:44:24.680 --> 00:44:26.870
I'm going to do everything I can to be

00:44:26.880 --> 00:44:28.750
as far away from the world and what they

00:44:28.760 --> 00:44:31.910
want and what they think is cool.

00:44:31.920 --> 00:44:34.270
I want to be as close as I can to Him,

00:44:34.280 --> 00:44:36.550
sitting in His lap, listening to His

00:44:36.560 --> 00:44:40.070
breath. What can I do to be closer to

00:44:40.080 --> 00:44:43.555
Him? I'm not just right on the edge

00:44:43.565 --> 00:44:45.310
of living in the world

00:44:45.320 --> 00:44:48.349
and barely in the church;

00:44:48.359 --> 00:44:50.430
I want to be all in.

00:44:50.440 --> 00:44:53.070
I want to know what

00:44:53.080 --> 00:44:54.950
His breath smells like if He has

00:44:54.960 --> 00:44:56.750
breath. If He has bad breath that day,

00:44:56.760 --> 00:44:58.790
which I'm sure He doesn't, but if He

00:44:58.800 --> 00:45:02.630
did, I want to know that He did,

00:45:02.640 --> 00:45:04.070
or what kind of fragrance He

00:45:04.070 --> 00:45:04.080
had.

00:45:04.080 --> 00:45:06.270
'Did you spray some cologne on,

00:45:06.280 --> 00:45:08.070
Lord? I want to know what You have on

00:45:08.080 --> 00:45:09.910
today.

00:45:09.920 --> 00:45:12.550
What is it? Is it frankincense

00:45:12.550 --> 00:45:12.560
today?'I

00:45:12.560 --> 00:45:14.030
want that

00:45:14.030 --> 00:45:14.040
because

00:45:14.040 --> 00:45:18.190
I'm that close.

00:45:18.200 --> 00:45:22.630
I just want to know Him.

00:45:22.640 --> 00:45:24.710
And I know that when you seek Him, you

00:45:24.720 --> 00:45:27.110
will find Him

00:45:27.120 --> 00:45:29.030
because I have those moments like I had

00:45:29.040 --> 00:45:30.430
last night.

00:45:30.440 --> 00:45:33.790
And I could see all that was coming.

00:45:33.800 --> 00:45:35.510
And after it was over, the presence

00:45:35.520 --> 00:45:38.190
filled me. I could feel it all day today

00:45:38.200 --> 00:45:40.750
quietly.

00:45:40.760 --> 00:45:43.110
I learned to get quieter as I talked

00:45:43.120 --> 00:45:45.750
to my friend Billy Burke.

00:45:45.760 --> 00:45:48.550
He's not a chatterbox.

00:45:48.560 --> 00:45:51.150
He stays to himself, and you learn from

00:45:51.160 --> 00:45:53.510
people who walk with Him.

00:45:53.520 --> 00:45:55.349
What does it take?

00:45:55.359 --> 00:45:57.990
And what

00:45:58.000 --> 00:46:00.510
does God say about you

00:46:00.520 --> 00:46:02.430
whenever I get off the phone with you?

00:46:02.440 --> 00:46:05.150
Not that I'm perfect, but it's always a

00:46:05.160 --> 00:46:07.070
fragrance.

00:46:07.080 --> 00:46:09.390
What is the

00:46:09.400 --> 00:46:10.910
fragrance that you leave in His

00:46:10.920 --> 00:46:14.070
nostrils?

00:46:14.080 --> 00:46:17.110
Does He call you friend?

00:46:17.120 --> 00:46:20.150
I love it whenever the Lord says to me,

00:46:20.160 --> 00:46:24.349
'Billy's my

00:46:24.349 --> 00:46:24.359
friend.'Walk

00:46:24.359 --> 00:46:26.670
carefully

00:46:26.680 --> 00:46:29.270
when you talk that way to Him. 'He's my

00:46:29.280 --> 00:46:31.430
friend.'It

00:46:31.440 --> 00:46:33.550
challenges me.

00:46:33.560 --> 00:46:36.030
I go,

00:46:36.040 --> 00:46:37.710
'He's Your

00:46:37.720 --> 00:46:40.870
friend.'Honor

00:46:40.880 --> 00:46:43.110
Him when you're on the phone. Say

00:46:43.120 --> 00:46:44.790
this. Don't say that. Don't ever say

00:46:44.800 --> 00:46:46.750
that. Don't disrespect Him. He corrects

00:46:46.760 --> 00:46:48.310
me about certain things, and I'm just

00:46:48.310 --> 00:46:48.320
a

00:46:48.320 --> 00:46:50.349
young guy. Some things,

00:46:50.359 --> 00:46:51.990
like I said earlier, just dumb things

00:46:52.000 --> 00:46:53.630
sometimes come out of your mouth when

00:46:53.640 --> 00:46:55.470
you chatter. You talk to

00:46:55.480 --> 00:46:57.030
somebody that's older and the Lord

00:46:57.040 --> 00:47:02.550
says,

00:47:02.560 --> 00:47:04.510
'Hush.'What

00:47:04.520 --> 00:47:07.670
does the Father think about you?

00:47:07.680 --> 00:47:09.349
What is the fragrance that you leave

00:47:09.359 --> 00:47:17.230
around Him?

00:47:17.240 --> 00:47:20.070
I want so badly for Him

00:47:20.070 --> 00:47:20.080
to want

00:47:20.080 --> 00:47:22.950
to visit my house

00:47:22.960 --> 00:47:25.710
and feel comfortable here,

00:47:25.710 --> 00:47:25.720
where

00:47:25.720 --> 00:47:27.390
He says, 'You know what? I can go

00:47:27.400 --> 00:47:28.710
there

00:47:28.720 --> 00:47:33.030
and I know I won't be grieved.

00:47:33.040 --> 00:47:37.990
Take not Thy Spirit from

00:47:37.990 --> 00:47:38.000
me.'Kathryn

00:47:38.000 --> 00:47:39.630
Kuhlman used to say things like

00:47:39.640 --> 00:47:41.310
that, and I thought she sounded kind of

00:47:41.320 --> 00:47:43.230
nutty

00:47:43.240 --> 00:47:45.510
because I was ignorant.

00:47:45.520 --> 00:47:47.470
But the older I get

00:47:47.470 --> 00:47:47.480
and

00:47:47.480 --> 00:47:50.270
the more I spend at His feet, I realize

00:47:50.280 --> 00:47:52.070
there is—like I said, I can feel it when

00:47:52.080 --> 00:47:53.830
He withdraws like that

00:47:53.840 --> 00:47:55.670
when I said that about the redhead

00:47:55.680 --> 00:47:57.630
thing.

00:47:57.640 --> 00:47:59.510
I went,

00:47:59.520 --> 00:48:01.070
'Oh,

00:48:01.080 --> 00:48:04.349
I grieved it. It's not

00:48:04.359 --> 00:48:05.630
right.'Repent.

00:48:05.640 --> 00:48:07.910
Be sensitive.

00:48:07.920 --> 00:48:10.710
And the more you spend time with Him,

00:48:10.720 --> 00:48:13.390
your words are heavy and they have a lot

00:48:13.400 --> 00:48:15.190
of weight.

00:48:15.200 --> 00:48:17.550
And you'll learn you just can't

00:48:17.560 --> 00:48:22.310
flap your mouth all the time,

00:48:22.320 --> 00:48:25.550
especially having Him around.

00:48:25.560 --> 00:48:28.710
He has an opinion about everything.

00:48:28.720 --> 00:48:30.349
The Lord has an opinion about

00:48:30.359 --> 00:48:32.710
everything. And He says,

00:48:32.720 --> 00:48:34.510
'Think on these things: whatsoever

00:48:34.520 --> 00:48:35.990
things are lovely, whatsoever things are

00:48:36.000 --> 00:48:37.990
pure, whatsoever things are of good report.'I

00:48:37.990 --> 00:48:38.000
could

00:48:38.000 --> 00:48:41.030
go on and on. In 1 Corinthians

00:48:41.040 --> 00:48:43.230
13,

00:48:43.240 --> 00:48:45.110
love takes no account of a

00:48:45.110 --> 00:48:45.120
suffered

00:48:45.120 --> 00:48:46.390
wrong. I don't know how many times

00:48:46.390 --> 00:48:46.400
He

00:48:46.400 --> 00:48:51.070
corrects me about love.

00:48:51.080 --> 00:48:54.070
But faith works by love, and God is

00:48:54.080 --> 00:48:55.110
love,

00:48:55.120 --> 00:48:56.750
and the greater part

00:48:56.760 --> 00:48:59.270
of the anointing is walking in love.

00:49:01.600 --> 00:49:03.750
The angels visited. I remember I told

00:49:03.760 --> 00:49:04.710
you

00:49:04.720 --> 00:49:07.750
they said that he doesn't realize

00:49:07.750 --> 00:49:07.760
that

00:49:07.760 --> 00:49:11.030
most of what

00:49:11.040 --> 00:49:13.510
he gets before the Father,

00:49:13.520 --> 00:49:15.310
he'll be judged upon—what he's

00:49:15.320 --> 00:49:18.230
judged upon the most—is: how did he walk

00:49:18.240 --> 00:49:19.830
in love? How did he treat his fellow

00:49:19.840 --> 00:49:21.910
brethren?

00:49:21.920 --> 00:49:26.790
How did he walk in love?

00:49:26.800 --> 00:49:31.190
How did you treat people

00:49:31.200 --> 00:49:33.710
when you think you're better than them?

00:49:33.720 --> 00:49:35.390
Do you bless them?

00:49:35.400 --> 00:49:38.630
Do you help the waiter out at the table

00:49:38.640 --> 00:49:40.430
that's serving you,

00:49:40.440 --> 00:49:42.590
and they

00:49:42.600 --> 00:49:45.310
may have had a rough day?

00:49:45.320 --> 00:49:46.990
Do you treat them with honor and give

00:49:47.000 --> 00:49:48.710
them a good tip, or do you just

00:49:48.720 --> 00:49:50.670
give a little bit?

00:49:50.680 --> 00:49:51.990
'Here's a

00:49:51.990 --> 00:49:52.000
buck.'What

00:49:52.000 --> 00:49:55.710
are you going to do with a dollar?

00:49:55.720 --> 00:49:58.470
She has to feed her family.

00:49:58.480 --> 00:50:00.550
If you can't afford to give a tip,

00:50:00.560 --> 00:50:03.750
don't go out to eat then.

00:50:03.750 --> 00:50:03.760
I

00:50:03.760 --> 00:50:07.430
say go through the drive-thru,

00:50:07.440 --> 00:50:11.390
but don't treat people bad.

00:50:11.400 --> 00:50:14.110
I always try to walk in love.

00:50:14.120 --> 00:50:15.550
I'm not always saying that I've been

00:50:15.560 --> 00:50:16.750
good at that,

00:50:16.760 --> 00:50:18.390
but the Lord rebukes me about certain

00:50:18.400 --> 00:50:21.190
things now. And He'll say, 'Brandon,

00:50:21.200 --> 00:50:23.230
that's a poverty mentality.

00:50:23.240 --> 00:50:24.630
What you're doing and how you just acted

00:50:24.640 --> 00:50:28.430
right then is

00:50:28.430 --> 00:50:28.440
poverty.'I

00:50:28.440 --> 00:50:29.750
say,

00:50:29.760 --> 00:50:31.590
'Break poverty.'It's a mindset. It's a

00:50:31.600 --> 00:50:33.390
stronghold.

00:50:33.400 --> 00:50:38.070
Break poverty off of your life

00:50:38.080 --> 00:50:43.150
by how you think and how you act,

00:50:43.160 --> 00:50:45.230
how you sow,

00:50:45.240 --> 00:50:46.270
what you're believing, what you're

00:50:46.280 --> 00:50:51.750
saying.

00:50:51.760 --> 00:50:54.030
So

00:50:54.040 --> 00:50:55.870
when I saw it last night and I saw

00:50:55.880 --> 00:50:57.710
all that, I

00:50:57.720 --> 00:51:00.550
was

00:51:00.550 --> 00:51:00.560
bothered—not

00:51:00.560 --> 00:51:02.950
because of what I saw, but

00:51:02.960 --> 00:51:04.590
because there are so many of you that have

00:51:04.600 --> 00:51:09.110
no idea what's coming

00:51:09.120 --> 00:51:11.430
and you're not ready.

00:51:11.440 --> 00:51:14.950
And I've tried so hard to convey to you:

00:51:14.960 --> 00:51:16.270
it's time for you to learn how to

00:51:16.280 --> 00:51:19.630
believe God for five

00:51:19.630 --> 00:51:19.640
dollars.

00:51:19.640 --> 00:51:22.350
It's time for you to

00:51:22.360 --> 00:51:25.270
believe—what

00:51:25.280 --> 00:51:26.990
if there was no way for you to go

00:51:27.000 --> 00:51:29.390
get a surgery

00:51:29.400 --> 00:51:32.230
and you really needed it?

00:51:32.240 --> 00:51:34.870
Can you believe God for a toenail that

00:51:34.880 --> 00:51:37.550
hurts?

00:51:37.550 --> 00:51:37.560
When

00:51:37.560 --> 00:51:39.710
it

00:51:39.720 --> 00:51:41.230
comes down to it

00:51:41.240 --> 00:51:42.870
and we're in

00:51:42.880 --> 00:51:44.950
the end times and we see these things

00:51:44.960 --> 00:51:47.030
around us, could I believe for the

00:51:47.030 --> 00:51:47.040
impossible—the

00:51:47.040 --> 00:51:48.430
surgery—that

00:51:48.440 --> 00:51:50.670
God would come

00:51:50.680 --> 00:51:52.590
through?

00:51:52.600 --> 00:51:55.390
I saw people around tables that had

00:51:55.400 --> 00:51:57.870
nothing,

00:51:57.880 --> 00:52:00.030
and they would

00:52:00.040 --> 00:52:02.830
hold their hands. I saw pots of food

00:52:02.840 --> 00:52:05.030
fill up with

00:52:05.040 --> 00:52:07.670
beans and cornbread and

00:52:07.680 --> 00:52:09.990
potatoes.

00:52:10.000 --> 00:52:12.430
I saw families that had

00:52:12.440 --> 00:52:14.990
steaming pots of food within just

00:52:15.000 --> 00:52:17.990
seconds when they gave grace.

00:52:18.000 --> 00:52:20.830
God showed up and did a miracle.

00:52:20.840 --> 00:52:22.630
Now, I've heard of other people having

00:52:22.640 --> 00:52:24.870
the same kind of visions,

00:52:24.880 --> 00:52:26.470
but the Lord warned me and He said,

00:52:26.480 --> 00:52:27.950
'Brandon,

00:52:27.960 --> 00:52:30.390
the Bible says I've never seen

00:52:30.400 --> 00:52:31.830
the righteous forsaken or a seed

00:52:31.840 --> 00:52:33.750
begging bread.

00:52:33.760 --> 00:52:35.750
Either you believe it or you don't.'George Mueller was

00:52:35.760 --> 00:52:37.630
one of them.

00:52:37.640 --> 00:52:39.990
He had the orphanages and all this.

00:52:40.000 --> 00:52:42.030
He would start out believing for

00:52:42.030 --> 00:52:42.040
five

00:52:42.040 --> 00:52:44.070
dollars,

00:52:44.080 --> 00:52:46.310
and then he said it was just as

00:52:46.320 --> 00:52:48.550
easy to believe for five dollars as it was

00:52:48.560 --> 00:52:51.190
for a million later on in his walk

00:52:51.200 --> 00:52:53.190
with the Lord. So he could believe for

00:52:53.200 --> 00:52:54.910
a million dollars

00:52:54.920 --> 00:52:56.670
or he could believe for five dollars, but it was

00:52:56.680 --> 00:52:58.350
the same amount of faith after a while.

00:52:58.360 --> 00:53:02.510
He built himself up to it.

00:53:02.520 --> 00:53:04.150
So a million dollars wasn't much for him

00:53:04.160 --> 00:53:07.350
anymore, just like five bucks.

00:53:07.360 --> 00:53:08.990
But it took

00:53:09.000 --> 00:53:11.950
faith and patience. Faith works.

00:53:11.960 --> 00:53:13.990
Work it. Faith without works is

00:53:14.000 --> 00:53:15.070
dead.

00:53:15.080 --> 00:53:16.390
So,

00:53:16.400 --> 00:53:17.710
all right, I've talked too much again

00:53:17.720 --> 00:53:18.910
tonight,

00:53:18.920 --> 00:53:21.030
but I've tried to warn you all.

00:53:21.040 --> 00:53:22.630
You better start

00:53:22.640 --> 00:53:24.910
activating your faith.

00:53:24.920 --> 00:53:28.070
Believe God for the impossible.

00:53:28.080 --> 00:53:30.830
Get in the Word. Faith cometh by hearing

00:53:30.840 --> 00:53:33.150
and hearing by the Word of God. That's the only

00:53:33.160 --> 00:53:35.590
way faith comes. 'Well, I bet

00:53:35.600 --> 00:53:39.270
if I had visitations from Jesus, if

00:53:39.280 --> 00:53:41.630
I had visitations from angels and all

00:53:41.640 --> 00:53:43.190
the things that you say you've had,

00:53:43.200 --> 00:53:46.670
Brandon, I bet I'd have great

00:53:46.670 --> 00:53:46.680
faith.'No,

00:53:46.680 --> 00:53:48.510
it

00:53:48.520 --> 00:53:50.870
had nothing to do with it.

00:53:50.880 --> 00:53:54.390
Because the moment you have challenges,

00:53:54.400 --> 00:53:56.670
you doubt those things and it comes up

00:53:56.680 --> 00:53:58.030
in your heart. The only thing that ever

00:53:58.040 --> 00:54:00.349
keeps me anchored is the word of God.

00:54:00.359 --> 00:54:02.870
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by

00:54:02.880 --> 00:54:06.510
the word of God—not an experience.

00:54:06.520 --> 00:54:07.870
I don't care what kind of great

00:54:07.880 --> 00:54:10.790
experience you've had. If you don't have

00:54:10.800 --> 00:54:12.270
the word of God down inside of your

00:54:12.280 --> 00:54:14.710
heart, whenever the storms of life come,

00:54:14.720 --> 00:54:17.150
the experience never will keep you. The

00:54:17.160 --> 00:54:19.590
word will.

00:54:19.600 --> 00:54:25.110
And I've seen Jesus nine times now.

00:54:26.440 --> 00:54:27.830
He visits

00:54:27.840 --> 00:54:29.510
and I'll talk to him,

00:54:29.520 --> 00:54:32.670
and I don't say that to brag.

00:54:32.680 --> 00:54:34.030
It's more than

00:54:34.040 --> 00:54:36.030
that now.

00:54:36.040 --> 00:54:37.750
Because he stood

00:54:37.760 --> 00:54:40.710
here—he

00:54:40.720 --> 00:54:42.630
came to the house

00:54:42.640 --> 00:54:44.750
twice.

00:54:44.760 --> 00:54:47.070
So over the course of my life now, it's

00:54:47.080 --> 00:54:49.349
going on a lot.

00:54:49.359 --> 00:54:51.910
Why, Brandon? Why you? I don't

00:54:51.920 --> 00:54:53.230
know.

00:54:53.240 --> 00:54:54.830
He'll visit any one of you if you seek

00:54:54.840 --> 00:54:57.750
him.

00:54:57.760 --> 00:55:00.630
I'm just thankful when he does.

00:55:00.640 --> 00:55:02.270
How many angels?

00:55:02.280 --> 00:55:03.590
This is the thing I never tell you. You

00:55:03.600 --> 00:55:05.790
know how many times I see demons?

00:55:05.800 --> 00:55:07.870
More than I see the other, but I never

00:55:07.880 --> 00:55:09.710
talk about it.

00:55:09.720 --> 00:55:12.910
In fact, I saw three today,

00:55:12.920 --> 00:55:17.630
but I don't talk about it.

00:55:17.640 --> 00:55:19.270
Why give glory to something that's

00:55:19.280 --> 00:55:20.349
fallen

00:55:20.359 --> 00:55:22.870
and has already been defeated with your

00:55:22.880 --> 00:55:26.270
words? Why give them power in

00:55:26.280 --> 00:55:28.470
your words? The more you exalt

00:55:28.470 --> 00:55:28.480
them—they're

00:55:28.480 --> 00:55:30.710
exalted by pride—and the more

00:55:30.720 --> 00:55:32.030
you talk about them, they fluff

00:55:32.040 --> 00:55:34.190
themselves up. Why? Because that's what

00:55:34.200 --> 00:55:35.910
they're after.

00:55:35.920 --> 00:55:39.070
They want you to acknowledge them.

00:55:39.080 --> 00:55:41.030
And the more you acknowledge them—'I see

00:55:41.040 --> 00:55:42.470
a demon there! I see a demon

00:55:42.470 --> 00:55:42.480
there!'—they

00:55:42.480 --> 00:55:44.790
go, 'Oh, you do? You see

00:55:44.790 --> 00:55:44.800
me?'and

00:55:44.800 --> 00:55:46.390
they get all excited about it

00:55:46.400 --> 00:55:48.710
because

00:55:48.720 --> 00:55:51.349
it's all about pride.

00:55:51.359 --> 00:55:53.110
Do you see?

00:55:53.120 --> 00:55:54.990
And so many Christians focus on the

00:55:55.000 --> 00:55:57.750
demonic way too much.

00:55:57.760 --> 00:56:00.510
I don't talk about it

00:56:00.520 --> 00:56:02.470
very long. And the same thing about

00:56:02.480 --> 00:56:04.830
witchcraft: I take authority over it and

00:56:04.830 --> 00:56:04.840
I'll

00:56:04.840 --> 00:56:07.230
leave it alone.

00:56:07.240 --> 00:56:10.710
Hexes and vexes and all that—it's real.

00:56:10.720 --> 00:56:13.710
But they don't have power over me.

00:56:13.720 --> 00:56:16.510
A curse without a cause cannot stand.

00:56:16.520 --> 00:56:18.510
Greater is he that is in me than he that

00:56:18.520 --> 00:56:20.790
is in the world. A thousand shall fall

00:56:20.800 --> 00:56:22.349
at our side and 10,000 on our right

00:56:22.359 --> 00:56:24.390
hand, but nothing shall come nigh us.

00:56:24.400 --> 00:56:26.190
Either you believe it or you

00:56:26.200 --> 00:56:27.470
don't.

00:56:27.480 --> 00:56:29.430
And this covenant

00:56:29.440 --> 00:56:31.670
of his blood and what he did for us on

00:56:31.680 --> 00:56:33.870
that cross—I am seated with him in the

00:56:33.880 --> 00:56:35.390
heavenlies.

00:56:35.400 --> 00:56:37.110
And when you understand and you're a

00:56:37.120 --> 00:56:39.470
believing believer and you walk in the

00:56:39.480 --> 00:56:41.670
authority of the believer, nothing shall

00:56:41.680 --> 00:56:44.030
by any means hurt you. And I say to be

00:56:44.040 --> 00:56:45.590
absent from the body is to be present

00:56:45.600 --> 00:56:46.870
with the Lord.

00:56:46.880 --> 00:56:51.070
I have victory no matter what.

00:56:52.560 --> 00:56:54.990
So when I tell you I see demonic stuff,

00:56:55.000 --> 00:56:56.349
yes,

00:56:56.359 --> 00:56:58.750
but they're defeated.

00:56:58.760 --> 00:57:00.550
So why talk about something that's been

00:57:00.560 --> 00:57:04.369
defeated?

00:57:05.200 --> 00:57:06.270
And all these people talking about

00:57:06.270 --> 00:57:06.280
singing

00:57:06.280 --> 00:57:08.470
angels and talking

00:57:08.470 --> 00:57:08.480
angels—I

00:57:08.480 --> 00:57:10.310
don't believe it.

00:57:11.880 --> 00:57:14.590
Do you know? They are always on

00:57:14.600 --> 00:57:16.950
assignment to give him glory.

00:57:16.960 --> 00:57:19.870
They don't ever bring glory to

00:57:19.870 --> 00:57:19.880
themselves.

00:57:19.880 --> 00:57:22.030
Never.

00:57:22.040 --> 00:57:25.390
They always are looking to him.

00:57:25.400 --> 00:57:27.870
Every time I've had it, they always are

00:57:27.880 --> 00:57:29.830
looking to him

00:57:29.840 --> 00:57:32.670
unless they have a word to tell you. And

00:57:32.680 --> 00:57:34.070
the other night, he had an opal

00:57:34.080 --> 00:57:36.670
outfit and he stood right over here.

00:57:36.680 --> 00:57:38.070
He was on assignment. He gave me a

00:57:38.080 --> 00:57:39.870
message; he told me what he was supposed to

00:57:39.880 --> 00:57:43.470
say. But the moment he stopped speaking,

00:57:43.480 --> 00:57:45.150
he didn't look at me like he wanted to

00:57:45.160 --> 00:57:47.590
have pie and coconut milk and a

00:57:47.590 --> 00:57:47.600
fistbump.

00:57:47.600 --> 00:57:50.310
He was looking to the Father

00:57:50.320 --> 00:57:52.070
immediately.

00:57:52.080 --> 00:57:55.310
His eyes were upon our Father, getting

00:57:55.320 --> 00:57:57.310
strength from him. And the moment the

00:57:57.320 --> 00:58:00.349
angels gaze upon our Lord, they get

00:58:00.359 --> 00:58:04.750
strength. Their skin glows.

00:58:04.760 --> 00:58:07.950
They glow because of the glory.

00:58:07.960 --> 00:58:10.870
So if they're always looking to him

00:58:10.880 --> 00:58:13.550
and they're around him all the time,

00:58:13.560 --> 00:58:15.590
how much more should you be looking at

00:58:15.600 --> 00:58:16.830
him

00:58:16.840 --> 00:58:19.870
as his child?

00:58:19.880 --> 00:58:22.390
They never have a mission of their

00:58:22.400 --> 00:58:23.790
own.

00:58:29.040 --> 00:58:31.030
They're on a mission from him to help

00:58:31.040 --> 00:58:31.910
you.

00:58:31.920 --> 00:58:34.270
They're ministering spirits sent forth

00:58:34.280 --> 00:58:39.990
to the heirs of salvation.

00:58:39.990 --> 00:58:40.000
That's

00:58:40.000 --> 00:58:41.590
what the Bible says.

00:58:41.600 --> 00:58:43.110
And then it says we can entertain

00:58:43.120 --> 00:58:45.070
angels unaware. Why? Because they're on

00:58:45.080 --> 00:58:46.870
an assignment.

00:58:46.880 --> 00:58:48.590
Things can happen

00:58:48.600 --> 00:58:50.870
because he's sent his angels to keep

00:58:50.880 --> 00:58:52.710
charge over us, lest

00:58:52.720 --> 00:58:54.270
they bear us up in their hands, lest

00:58:54.280 --> 00:58:56.430
we dash our foot against a

00:58:56.430 --> 00:58:56.440
stone—Psalm

00:58:56.440 --> 00:59:00.190
91.

00:59:00.200 --> 00:59:01.910
And I believe it.

00:59:01.920 --> 00:59:05.110
But demons, they're different.

00:59:05.120 --> 00:59:06.710
They are always about themselves. They're

00:59:06.720 --> 00:59:08.110
always wanting attention. They always

00:59:08.120 --> 00:59:09.950
want you to be in fear.

00:59:09.960 --> 00:59:12.670
Fear tolerated is faith contaminated.

00:59:12.680 --> 00:59:14.550
The more you fear them, the more it is faith in

00:59:14.550 --> 00:59:14.560
their

00:59:14.560 --> 00:59:17.030
ability to hurt you. You have

00:59:17.040 --> 00:59:19.510
more faith in their ability to hurt you

00:59:19.520 --> 00:59:21.790
than in God's ability to protect you. Fear

00:59:21.800 --> 00:59:24.510
tolerated is faith contaminated. And they

00:59:24.520 --> 00:59:27.510
will present themselves to you as big as

00:59:27.520 --> 00:59:30.710
they can so that you'll gaze upon them

00:59:30.720 --> 00:59:33.270
instead of our Lord Jesus. And the more

00:59:33.280 --> 00:59:35.430
you look at a demon, the more they will

00:59:35.440 --> 00:59:37.710
get bigger in front of you because

00:59:37.720 --> 00:59:41.470
they're full of pride.

00:59:41.480 --> 00:59:45.310
It's all about them.

00:59:45.320 --> 00:59:46.430
So if you ever want to know if you're

00:59:46.440 --> 00:59:48.550
really talking to a demon versus an angel,

00:59:48.560 --> 00:59:50.510
always look at them if they're around

00:59:50.520 --> 00:59:52.110
you. Look and say, 'Well, I see this.

00:59:52.120 --> 00:59:53.830
What are they doing?'They're looking to

00:59:53.840 --> 00:59:56.630
the Father.

00:59:56.640 --> 00:59:58.230
Angels—demons

00:59:58.240 --> 01:00:04.496
just want to be exalted.

01:00:06.280 --> 01:00:08.670
Does that help you a little bit?

01:00:08.680 --> 01:00:09.950
So, there's some of you that

01:00:09.950 --> 01:00:09.960
are

01:00:09.960 --> 01:00:12.430
having things knocking on your house,

01:00:12.440 --> 01:00:13.870
waking you up in the middle of the night

01:00:13.880 --> 01:00:15.910
with cold chills—something

01:00:15.910 --> 01:00:15.920
of

01:00:15.920 --> 01:00:18.430
fear.

01:00:18.440 --> 01:00:20.070
You are tormented all the time by

01:00:20.080 --> 01:00:21.990
demonic spirits.

01:00:22.000 --> 01:00:24.790
Anoint your house with oil and tell that

01:00:24.800 --> 01:00:28.470
devil to get out. Open the door

01:00:28.480 --> 01:00:32.150
and say, 'You get out of here right now!

01:00:32.160 --> 01:00:35.750
You're not welcome in my house.'But

01:00:35.750 --> 01:00:35.760
there are

01:00:35.760 --> 01:00:37.110
so many people who play

01:00:37.110 --> 01:00:37.120
pat-a-cake

01:00:37.120 --> 01:00:40.030
with Casper.

01:00:40.040 --> 01:00:41.750
And you think, 'Well, it's

01:00:41.760 --> 01:00:44.550
just Grandpa.'No, it's a familiar

01:00:44.560 --> 01:00:47.270
spirit. The Bible says to be absent

01:00:47.280 --> 01:00:48.830
from the body is to be present with the

01:00:48.840 --> 01:00:50.510
Lord. You don't have Grandpa hanging

01:00:50.520 --> 01:00:52.190
around your house.

01:00:52.200 --> 01:00:53.630
You don't have Grandma hanging around

01:00:53.640 --> 01:00:55.230
your house, and it's not your cousin

01:00:55.240 --> 01:00:56.910
either.

01:00:56.920 --> 01:00:58.990
Do you understand? It is a familiar

01:00:59.000 --> 01:01:01.750
spirit.

01:01:01.760 --> 01:01:03.910
It is something that was assigned and

01:01:03.920 --> 01:01:06.150
was there watching them

01:01:06.160 --> 01:01:08.230
and is trying to imitate them. It's not

01:01:08.240 --> 01:01:09.630
them.

01:01:09.640 --> 01:01:11.190
They're either with Jesus or they're in

01:01:11.200 --> 01:01:14.150
hell. There is no

01:01:14.150 --> 01:01:14.160
in-between.

01:01:14.160 --> 01:01:15.910
They're not locked in an alternate

01:01:15.920 --> 01:01:18.070
universe and they're trapped.

01:01:18.080 --> 01:01:19.830
Either you're with him or you're in

01:01:19.840 --> 01:01:21.510
hell.

01:01:21.520 --> 01:01:23.310
So stop playing around.

01:01:23.320 --> 01:01:24.910
There's no demonic spirit hanging out at

01:01:24.920 --> 01:01:27.150
your house—Uncle Freddy or whoever

01:01:27.160 --> 01:01:29.430
that's up there trying to talk to you

01:01:29.430 --> 01:01:29.440
through

01:01:29.440 --> 01:01:31.750
Ouija boards and doing weird stuff.

01:01:31.760 --> 01:01:33.470
'Oh, this is your cousin Al.

01:01:33.480 --> 01:01:35.070
He's telling you something in a message

01:01:35.080 --> 01:01:39.990
on a Ouija board.'That's a demon.

01:01:40.000 --> 01:01:43.190
That's not cousin Al.

01:01:43.200 --> 01:01:45.190
And people play around with

01:01:45.190 --> 01:01:45.200
stuff—black

01:01:45.200 --> 01:01:47.150
magic, warlocks doing chicken

01:01:47.160 --> 01:01:49.230
spells, drinking blood, and doing

01:01:49.240 --> 01:01:50.990
all kinds of things that they

01:01:50.990 --> 01:01:51.000
think—and

01:01:51.000 --> 01:01:51.790
they're

01:01:51.800 --> 01:01:53.350
trying to get those devils to help them

01:01:53.360 --> 01:01:55.670
out. But guess what? The very devils you

01:01:55.680 --> 01:01:58.030
think you control are going to drag your

01:01:58.040 --> 01:02:02.390
soul to hell.

01:02:02.400 --> 01:02:04.590
They're using you

01:02:04.600 --> 01:02:07.310
as an apparatus into this earth because

01:02:07.320 --> 01:02:09.590
they are not able to express themselves

01:02:09.600 --> 01:02:12.430
without a human being.

01:02:12.440 --> 01:02:14.030
And they come inside of you to possess

01:02:14.040 --> 01:02:15.750
you. They're able to express

01:02:15.760 --> 01:02:18.230
themselves through a body,

01:02:18.240 --> 01:02:19.910
and people are stupid and they yield to

01:02:19.920 --> 01:02:22.590
them.

01:02:22.600 --> 01:02:25.590
So there you

01:02:25.590 --> 01:02:25.600
go—a

01:02:25.600 --> 01:02:28.550
little bit extra, I guess.

01:02:28.560 --> 01:02:30.230
God bless you all.

01:02:30.240 --> 01:02:32.510
Let's pray now.

01:02:32.520 --> 01:02:33.950
I don't know who that was for, but I

01:02:33.960 --> 01:02:36.510
felt to say it.

01:02:36.520 --> 01:02:39.270
Father, I thank you, Lord, for the body.

01:02:39.280 --> 01:02:41.790
You're so good to us, Father.

01:02:41.800 --> 01:02:43.510
And we're so thankful, Father, for all

01:02:43.520 --> 01:02:45.350
that you have done for

01:02:45.350 --> 01:02:45.360
us—that

